channel.title: Webclient!
channel.description:
I'm making a webclient for my server. I have one already but the issue is it had noclip on it and didn't know. I had a friend make my webclient and never did learn how to do it. I went on google and found some guides. When I looked at the tut. I tells me to find files and change them. I look for the files and there not there... I looked for the remake and the normal and can't find the ones I need.
I have a pi server but when I looked up some guides for pi it tells me the files I don't have.....
Anyone have a better guide thats not listed on google? or maybe someone can show me a tut. they used to learn how to do this..
